<!-- INTRO SECTION - BEGINS -->
	<section class="row">
		<div class="small-12 columns evo-spacer-padding-top-medium evo-site--pattern-library-intro">

{{# markdown }}
## {{ title }}
The Mercer color palette is designed to support a range of visual styles. These styles are all connected within a hierarchy that best defines the Mercer brand. These color palettes have been carefully crafted and are not meant to be customized further.
{{/ markdown }}

