{{# markdown }}
##### {{color-palette.primary}}
Mercer's primary "Sapphire" color palette communicates Mercer's personality and identity. This is the dominant color palette used for all Mercer branding, while the "Onyx" palette provides for additional flexibility with styling text, borders, and content dividers.
{{/ markdown }}
