{{# markdown }}
##### {{color-palette.tertiary}}
Tertiary colors are to be predominantly used for data visualization, charting solutions, and tables. These colors should never be used to replace the primary and secondary color palettes.
{{/ markdown }}
						</div>

						{{#slice color-palette.data offset="8" limit="5"}}
