						<div class="evo-site-markdown-content-block">
{{# markdown }}
##### {{color-palette.system}}
The system colors are used for important, high-level information that may require the user to take action. This type of information is presented in a container that represents a positive, negative or attention value. While these containers are generally positioned at the top of a page as alerts, they can also appear within content containers.
{{/ markdown }}
